{"tid":1394381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望咁多位係未來嘅運動之中，要搵到自己嘅崗位","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:03:26.000Z","uid":281507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"87041723534abb481e524b5f85005d815e79a350","tid":1394381,"uid":281507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"其實除咗出去行前線之外，仲有好多野可以做。<br />\n網上宣傳係好重要，嚟緊嘅8月2號同8月5號嘅罷工，你share比你啲FD，都已經可以幫到好多。<br />\n<br />\n或者你可以幫一啲行前線嘅勇士，mon住啲live，幫佢哋諗一條逃生路線，但啲資訊一定要準確， 唔係就變相害咗人。<br />\n<br />\n依下個啲要有能力先好做<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/martfack/status/1155636832861769728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmartfack%2Fstatus%2F1155636832861769728&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIESIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=6ed02d0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmartfack%2Fstatus%2F1155636832861769728&h=71d19599\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/martfack/status/1155636832861769728</a><br />\n着好哂full gear先好做。<br />\n<br />\n如何想做急救人員，要睇咗先。<br />\n<br />\n杏林覺醒急救懶人包：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/FirstAidLazyPack2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FFirstAidLazyPack2&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIESIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=d5a98994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/FirstAidLazyPack2</a><br />\n化學品入眼的處理方法：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2410532812516597&amp;id=2087023804867501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2410532812516597%26id%3D2087023804867501&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIESIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=0d685db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2410532812516597&amp;id=2087023804867501</a><br />\n（醫學治眼）<br />\n香港人受傷須知：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/340133343328490/posts/351792132162611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F340133343328490%2Fposts%2F351792132162611&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIESIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=653cf296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/340133343328490/posts/351792132162611</a><br />\n<br />\n最後大家要記住我哋嘅目的係<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n#8月2號公務員罷工<br />\n#8月5號三罷<br />\n#香港人加油"},{"pid":"213f7776861f018b2f83ed72cbddbcf47a25d951","tid":1394381,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"}]}